    <p>We've tested and ranked the best cheap nicotine pouches available on SnusFriends, spotlighting the brands that deliver honest flavour, reliable nicotine strength, and solid texture at prices that won't drain your wallet. Whether you're budget-conscious or just starting out, this guide will help you find excellent value without settling for subpar quality.</p>

    <h2>Why Budget Nicotine Pouches Are Worth Your Time</h2>

    <p>The perception that cheap equals low quality is outdated in the nicotine pouch market. Several factors have democratised pouch manufacturing:</p>

    <ul>
