        <li><strong>Scale economies:</strong> Established manufacturers now produce budget lines using the same quality ingredients as premium tiers, just with less marketing spend.</li>
        <li><strong>Direct distribution:</strong> Buying direct from retailers like SnusFriends eliminates middleman markups — you benefit immediately.</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>Budget nicotine pouches deliver the same nicotine strength and quality as premium brands—the difference is marketing spend, not formulation.</strong> A €0.89 pouch from KUMA contains the same nicotine strength and moisture content as a €3.50 pouch from ZYN. The difference is often packaging, brand heritage, and advertising spend, not formulation. See our <a href="/blog/best-nicotine-pouches-2026">complete expert rankings</a> for direct brand comparisons.</p>

